data.description: This newly renovated mid century haven has everything you need inside and out to enjoy life to the fullest! This lush refuge boasts a gorgeous swimming pool, a hot tub (which conveys), new pergolas, a freshly painted and expanded storage shed with a new roof and a potting station in the rear,a great fire pit area,fabulous new landscaping in the front and the backyard, new pavers and stones, incredible outdoor lighting , new shutters, new front door and a new expansive circular driveway which provides plenty of parking for your guests. The inside of this oasis is just as special. The kitchen has been renovated
